---
title: Spanish Butter-Bean Stew with Fragrant Rice
description: Recipes like Chef Lizzie’s hearty and wholesome vegetarian stew make packing in your five-a-day easy. Butter beans are a great ingredient for bulking up stews as well as being a useful source of potassium. For the perfect protein combination of grain and bean, we’ve served this stew with fluffy basmati rice (the tip in step 2 will change your rice cooking game for good!). Topped with a crunchy almond salsa and a good squeeze of fresh lemon juice, this dish will nourish you from the inside out.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/spanish-butter-bean-stew-21a425a0-1bbfea8d.jpg
